<h1>Weekend Care</h1>

<p>*mealworms already weighed out, separate media from worms by filtering the media into trash*</p>

<h2>Things you need to do for weekend care:</h2>
<ol>
<li>Remove all dishes from <em>EVERY</em> cage - soak in bleach and dish soap minimum 10 minutes.</li>
<li>Provide fresh water to <em>EVERY</em> cage.</li>
<li>Feed bats as directed for each room:</li>
</ol>

<h3>Colony Room</h3>
<% if @colony_cages.length == 0 %>
No Colony bats to feed.
<% else %>
<% for cage in @colony_cages %>
<table>
<th>Name</th><th>Food</th>
<tr>
<td><%= cage.name %>
<td><%= cage.food %>
<tr>
</table>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<h3>Belfry</h3>
<% if @belfry_cages.length == 0 %>
No Belfry bats to feed.
<% else %>
<% for cage in @belfry_cages %>
<table>
<th>Name</th><th>Food</th>
<tr>
<td><%= cage.name %>
<td><%= cage.food %>
<tr>
</table>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<h3>Fruit Bats</h3>
<% if @fruitbat_cages.length == 0 %>
No fruit bats to feed.
<% else %>
<% for cage in @fruitbat_cages %>
<table>
<th>Name</th><th>Food</th>
<tr>
